  ],
  "remarks": "General Technology Group Dalian Machine Tool Import and Export Co., Ltd. is a Chinese company involved in the industrial sector. It acts as an intermediary for General Technology Group Dalian Machine Tool Co., Ltd., which, through the Stanko Group of companies, exports machine tools on the Russian market, including for use by the Russian military and industrial complex. Therefore, General Technology Group Dalian Machine Tool Co., Import and Export Co., Ltd. is supporting Russia’s military and industrial complex, including by being involved in the development, production or supply of military technology and equipment.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}